Package org.symphonyoss.client.services

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ChatListener
    Callback interface for message events on the Chat object.
    ChatServiceListener
    Callback listener for the ChatService providing detection for new chat conversations.
    ConnectionsEventListener  
    ConnectionsListener
    Callback listener for use with the ConnectionsService which will provide notification of external connection requests.
    MessageListener
    Callback listener for the MessageService publishing SymMessages.
    RoomEventListener
    Callback interface for room events
    RoomListener
    Callback interface for room events
    RoomServiceEventListener  
    RoomServiceListener  
    SymCache  
    SymUserCache
    User cache subsystem
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ChatService
    The chat service provides capabilities to construct and monitor chat conversations.
    ConnectionsService
    This service handles incoming connection requests and provides options for automatically accepting requests.
    MessageService
    MessageService listens for all messages for a given BOT identity, identifies the type (Message, Chat, Room) of message and then publishes the message registered listeners associated with type.
    RoomService
    The room service provides capabilities that support room access and events.
